data.description: Phenomenal opportunity to own a large home on a large lot w/ plenty of interior space. Great location proximate to downtown walk to restaurants, street fairs, fireworks & all the joy of downtown!  Large private room on the main floor, could be used as a family room, extra bedroom, office, or recreation room. Plus 4 bedrooms upstairs & bedroom on the main floor. Parking pad for 3 additional vehicles, shed & a garage, large front porch, new concrete,  new windows 2022, and new shower installed 2023. Appliances stay(ignitors on stove don' work you have to lite manually), Sold As- Is.  Immediate occupancy.  This is a great value on a great home! *City Inspection on file- Sold as- is*
